 《Rush》、《Bon Jovi》等影片的制片人彼得·柯林斯去世，享年 73 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-collins- Producer-for-rush-bon-jovi-and-more-dies-ged-73-3771172?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=peter-collins- 73 岁的《Bon-Jovi 和更多死亡》制作人Anagricel DuranMon, 01 Jul 2024 19:55:24 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3771172 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “‘我仍然能听到他说‘好吧，伙计们，从顶部开始……不要停下来！’我们爱你B”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-collins-producer-for-rush-bon-jovi-and-more-dies-aged-73-3771172">《Rush》、《Bon Jovi》等影片的制作人彼得·柯林斯 (Peter Collins) 去世，享年 73 岁</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">。</a></p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>曾与<a href="/artists/Rush">Rush</a>和<a href="/artists/Bon-Jovi">Bon Jovi</a>等人合作过的英国唱片制作人彼得·柯林斯 (Peter Collins) 去世，享年 73 岁。</p><p>据报道，这位制片人在与胰腺癌作斗争后在田纳西州纳什维尔的家中去世。柯林斯的作品包括 Rush 的《Power Windows》、Bon Jovi 的《These Days》、Queensryche 的《Operation: Mindcrime》、 <a href="/artists/Alice-Cooper">Alice Cooper</a>的《Hey Stoopid》、Gary Moore 的《After the War》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jewel">Jewel</a>的《Spirit》、 <a href="/artists/Rick-Astley">Rick Astley 的</a>《Spirit》。的“肖像”和超过 50 张其他专辑。</p><p> Rush 在其官方 Instagram 帖子中向制片人致敬。 “彼得·柯林斯是我们敬爱的四张专辑的制作人。首先是“Power Windows”（&#39;85），然后是“Hold Your Fire”（&#39;87）、“Counterparts”（&#39;93）和“Test For Echo”（&#39;96）。当我们巡演时，我们很高兴在纳什维尔见到他。他有着顽皮、灿烂的微笑和极强的幽默感。他将会被如此怀念……安息吧大先生，”标题写道。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8z1G6SptKG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" 